              ARTH 223 Introduction Italian Renaissance Art 1300-1500 (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-18290" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
