      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Art History              : Surveys the changing role of the artwork in Renaissance Italy in its social, political, and religious contexts.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Chriscinda Claire Henry (Fall)                  </p>

    
