      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Art History              : A critical survey of contemporary art and theory, from 1945 to the present focusing on pivotal issues such as anti-war politics, feminism, sexual diversity, AIDS awareness, discourse of multiculturalism, debates about modernism and postmodernism, post colonialism, technology, and globalization.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
